Output site/img/tui-oco.gif
Set Shell zsh
Set Width 1400
Set Height 800
Set FontSize 13
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 10

Type "cdcx tui"
Enter
Sleep 8s
Type "o"
Sleep 1s
Type "BTC"
Sleep 0.5s
Enter
Sleep 0.5s
Type "65000"
Sleep 0.5s
Tab
Sleep 0.5s
Type "75000"
Sleep 0.5s
Tab
Sleep 0.5s
Type "0.01"
Sleep 0.5s
Tab
Sleep 2s
Escape
Sleep 1s
Type "q"